Overview of Options

  1. htmlwidgets
    • < 1 yr old, very popular, maintained by Rstudio, used by Plotly
  2. googleVis
    • Really cool but data and plot are hosted on their platform
  3. rCharts
    • Predecessor to htmlwidgets
  4. ggvis
    • ggplot2 authors, based on old javascript library
